com.ing.software.ocr.OcrObjects

Class OcrText

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ing.software.ocr.OcrObjects.OcrText

  • public class OcrText
extends java.lang.Object
    Object that represents a block (a collection of lines of text), a line of text (a collection of words) or a word. This object is immutable.
    Author:
    Riccardo Zaglia

        public OcrText(OcrText tl,
               android.graphics.RectF srcImgRect,
               android.graphics.RectF dstImgRect)
        Create a new OcrText with dimensions converted from one bitmap space to another
        Parameters:
        tl - OcrText to convert
        srcImgRect - source bitmap space. Eg: optimized amount strip, from (0, 0)
        dstImgRect - destination space. Eg: amount strip in original bitmap space.
